&lt;p&gt;NexGen is the leading one stop service provider offering complete petrol station forecourt solutions, servicing major oil companies in East Africa. We are leaders in service, equipment supply and maintenance as well as project management and forecourt automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NexGen Fuelworks Kenya Limited is excited to announce openings for Technician Trainees to join our field service and maintenance team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title&lt;/strong&gt;: Technician Trainees&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: Nairobi, Nyeri, and Nakuru (with travel as required)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;About the Role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NexGen Fuelworks is seeking a motivated and eager-to-learn Technical Trainees to join our team. This role is ideal for fresh graduates with a Diploma in Mechanical or Mechatronics Engineering who are passionate about the Oil &amp;amp; Gas downstream sector. The internship provides hands-on exposure to fuel equipment, dispensing pumps, compressors, and related systems, supporting our field service and maintenance operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist technicians in installation, servicing, and maintenance of fuel equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support troubleshooting of mechanical and electrical issues at client sites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in site visits, inspections, and reporting activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain tools, equipment, and safety standards during fieldwork.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document and record daily job activities as guided by supervisors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn and apply industry best practices in Oil &amp;amp; Gas equipment maintenance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diploma in Electrical, Mechatronics, Mechanical Engineering or related.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience will be an added advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interest in the Oil &amp;amp; Gas downstream industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to learn and adapt to hands-on fieldwork.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible to travel frequently across different sites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good teamwork, communication, and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What We Offer&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical, on-the-job training with experienced professionals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to real-world field service operations in the Oil &amp;amp; Gas sector.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to grow into full-time technical roles within the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transport and field allowances as per company policy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

